				\begin{document}$${I}^{-}$$\end{document} many times but P-150 CE has better electrochemical stability and prolonged coexistence in the two types of redox species. While the displayed cyclic electrode retention of P-150 CE has a stability of 94% after 50 cycles, bare PEDOT CE lost 13% of its electrocatalytic activity.Figure 3
